articles.title: By the numbers: Gauff outlasts Kostyuk for first Australian Open semifinal - WTA Tennis
articles.description: No.4 seed Coco Gauff came from 5-1 down to win the first set against Marta Kostyuk but needed three sets to advance to the semifinals of the Australian Open.
